  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Description</h2>An incredible New Year's roguelike in the genre of Survival! Immerse yourself in the holiday atmosphere and hold out as long as possible from the hordes of Memes and defeat all the Bosses!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858110/extras/6e9d54618dd3b38372fc506a5531b5a5.poster.avif?t=1728662984\" width=610 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858110/extras/6e9d54618dd3b38372fc506a5531b5a5.webm?t=1728662984\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858110/extras/6e9d54618dd3b38372fc506a5531b5a5.mp4?t=1728662984\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>New Year's holiday atmosphere<br></li><li>Original meme enemies and bosses<br></li><li>Over 60 upgrade items that make your character stronger!<br></li><li>Endless survival mode and high difficulty. How long will you last?<br></li><li>A powerful New Year's soundtrack that gives strength and confidence!<br></li><li>High score table, fight for the title of the Best among other players!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858110/extras/1be65ead7934d2eb9873cbd291ef4130.poster.avif?t=1728662984\" width=610 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858110/extras/1be65ead7934d2eb9873cbd291ef4130.webm?t=1728662984\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858110/extras/1be65ead7934d2eb9873cbd291ef4130.mp4?t=1728662984\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
